"title": "7372: hands, laying on of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7372: hands, laying on of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An action of God or human beings, often understood to convey healing, blessing or the gift of the Holy Spirit. It also indicates the conferring of authority upon individuals for the purpose of ministry.</p>\n<h2>Laying on of hands and the communication of gifts</h2>\n<h3>Laying on of hands communicates God's blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:16\">MRK 10:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:15\">MAT 19:15</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:14-Gen48:20\">GEN 48:14–48:20</a></p>\n<h3>Laying on of hands conveys God's healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:40\">LUK 4:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:3\">MAT 8:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:41\">MRK 1:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:13\">LUK 5:13</a> <em>the man with leprosy</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:18\">MAT 9:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:23\">MRK 5:23</a> <em>Jairus' daughter</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:29-Matt9:30\">MAT 9:29–9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:5\">MRK 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:32-Mark7:35\">MRK 7:32–7:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:18\">MRK 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:13\">LUK 13:13</a> <em>the crippled woman</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:8\">ACT 28:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14\">JAS 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Laying on of hands conveys the gift of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:17\">ACT 8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">DEU 34:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:19\">ACT 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:17\">ACT 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">ACT 19:6</a></p>\n<h3>Laying on of hands conveys reassurance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:17\">REV 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:7\">MAT 17:7</a></p>\n<h2>Laying on of hands in commissioning for service</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:18-Num27:23\">NUM 27:18–27:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:10\">NUM 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">DEU 34:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:6\">ACT 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:3\">ACT 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:14\">1TI 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:22\">1TI 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:6\">2TI 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Laying on of hands in the OT sacrificial system</h2>\n<h3>Laying on of hands in sin offerings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:21\">LEV 16:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:10\">EXO 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev4:4\">LEV 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev4:15\">LEV 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:14\">LEV 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:23\">2CH 29:23</a></p>\n<h3>Laying on of hands in other offerings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:4\">LEV 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:15\">EXO 29:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:19\">EXO 29:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev3:1-Lev3:2\">LEV 3:1–3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:18\">LEV 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:22\">LEV 8:22</a></p>\n<h2>Laying on of hands without reference to God</h2>\n<h3>Laying hands on people with intent to harm</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:27\">GEN 37:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:19\">JOS 2:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:7\">1SA 23:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:9-1Sam26:11\">1SA 26:9–26:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:23\">1SA 26:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:14\">ISA 11:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:12\">LUK 21:12</a></p>\n<h3>Laying on of hands in punishment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:14\">LEV 24:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:21\">NEH 13:21</a></p>\n<h2>The metaphorical laying of God's hand on people</h2>\n<h3>God's hand brings favour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:8\">NEH 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:6\">EZR 7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:28\">EZR 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:18\">EZR 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:18\">NEH 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand brings protection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:31\">EZR 8:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:9\">EZR 7:9</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand brings prophetic revelation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:3\">EZK 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:14\">EZK 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:22\">EZK 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:1\">EZK 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:22\">EZK 33:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1\">EZK 37:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:1\">EZK 40:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand brings judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:4\">EXO 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:6-1Sam5:12\">1SA 5:6–5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:6\">JER 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:21\">EZK 39:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:11\">ACT 13:11</a></p>",
